headline: Linde Reports First-Quarter 2025 Results
summary: WOKING, England, May 01, 2025--Linde plc (Nasdaq: LIN) today reported first-quarter 2025 net income of $1,673 million and diluted earnings per share of $3.51, up 3% and 5% respectively. Excluding Linde AG purchase accounting impacts and other charges, adjusted net income was $1,880 million, up 3% versus prior year. Adjusted earnings per share was $3.95, 5% above prior year.
